r\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21780,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/01\/29\/peace-prophet-ten-fold\/","url_meta":{"origin":24471,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: Send peace upon the Prophet, receive it ten fold","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 29, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Talha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came to us one day with a cheerful face. We said, \u201cWe see you smiling.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, the angel came to me, and he said: O Muhammad, your Lord has asked if would you not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17537,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/09\/tasbih-tahmid-33-times\/","url_meta":{"origin":24471,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Glorify Allah 33 times after every prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The poor emigrants came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, saying, \u201cThe wealthy have taken the highest degrees and blessed ranks!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHow is that?\u201d They said, \u201cThey pray as we pray, they fast as we fast, they give in\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25289,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/22\/increase-dua-prophet-j